Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:00:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,積滿了苔蘚很滑  要小心點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.40,0:00:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.34,0:01:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龍大人是怎樣的神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為到現在為止誰都沒有見過他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:11.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,島上的主人們所保護的神究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.66,0:01:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有  和行人在一起就沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.29,0:01:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是海龍大人的叫聲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好滑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫聲停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:01:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龍大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龍大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的願望是傳達不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原因就是…海龍大人會先聽取我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是海龍大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龍大人  請務必實現我的願望…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對了  還帶了供奉用的紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還好這裡有根繩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鬍子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龍大人  請保佑行人能離開這島
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是地震嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等會再說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,入口被…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音  那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是鬍子  大概是海龍大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在我不知情的情況下好像不小心拉斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像拉斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  居然把海龍大人的鬍子給拽下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也太讓人吃驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會受到天罰的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本來就是因為你們太沒用了我才去阻礙他們祈願的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是失敗了偶然中拽下來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  這樣一來  海龍大人也不會保佑行人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,公子  也只能放棄離開島了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們看吧  這樣一來行人就屬於我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為何會變成綾音的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個和那個是兩回事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不會承認的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最終女婿大人會選擇你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的喜歡他的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:05:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是應該考慮究竟如何做才為女婿大人好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼對行人來說是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人正準備出海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻知姐 你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人能觀察到遠處的式神所看到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是送你到中途吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有海龍大人的保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼能帶小鈴去那麼危險的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸豬排也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不一起去的話才會擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前我就說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男人就該保護女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛來這島上的時候確實什麼都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但現在已經變得很可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:06:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不得不去救美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同樣  也不能讓小鈴深處險境
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一個人也沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴  非常感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  女婿大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能出海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓行人走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你真的覺得這樣做可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有…這樣做了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是女婿大人所盼望的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算失去生命也無所謂嗎
