Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龍大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龍大人  請保佑行人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小凜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴姐  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  為什麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從上面入口進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個炸開了一條路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想救行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能讓你一人把風頭全搶了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真囉嗦  我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不率直啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是不行  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…不是故意的  我真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.14,0:12:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龍大人  真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龍大人  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有願望…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龍大人  請保佑公子平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請保護行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請救救行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龍大人  請實現小鈴和行人的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:34.44,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龍大人  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請務必保護行人  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.84,0:14:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那光芒是…那就是海龍大人的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人現在已經在漩渦外面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是你所期望的嗎  西部的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虎才是  不是故意讓他通過的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的想法都是一致的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,女婿大人  如果能離開島的話  那並不是他一人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定是因為行人擁有能讓大家能為之如此付出的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這微妙的刺法有點難
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還…還以為要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說這裡是島外了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是來接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平安無事啊  收到信我很擔心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  這樣一來好像變成是哥哥遇難了我趕來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是好笑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:15:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  有精神就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  沒事真是萬幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是萬幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從剛才開始就很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實呢  在哥哥離家出走後我就馬上出海來找你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後所乘的船遇到暴風雨  沉入海底了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後  醒來的時候已經被漂流到一個不知名的島
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:18.49,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那島很有趣既沒有電視也沒有電話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做飯要用柴燒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魚也要自己釣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蔬菜有那麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  對了  那島叫藍蘭島
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,藍蘭島
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似是只有男人的島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後這些就是島民
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好人是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥的擔心是必然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別喊我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  我們沒有因不純的動機對美咲有過任何侵犯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有誰讓美咲悲傷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我很笨拙  但一直被大家所幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在非常的高興
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以還想再在藍蘭島生活一會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,飯也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽些奇聞也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  哥哥也一起過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很歡迎哥哥您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這暴風雨來之前不穿越漩渦的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回去是…要回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回我的 藍蘭島
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥的…藍蘭島
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡有人在等著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲  就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  也請小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快速出發
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  明明看得到島
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卻無論幾次都被推回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然從外面進去是絕對不可能的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要走
