Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要跟行人永別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.46,0:19:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看著吧  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不可能的事情是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對…沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是不行嗎
