Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.29,0:20:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暴風雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心女婿大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人絕對沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在一定見到妹妹美咲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忘記行人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也許還會有新的女婿大人會漂流進來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆婆  在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說曹操曹操就到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看  在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:20:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  又相見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,飛蛾撲火自取滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然自願回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第二回  爭奪女婿大人捉迷藏大會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  女婿大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:38.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爭奪女婿大人捉迷藏大會要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,規則就不用我介紹了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為何  我沒聽過這回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.73,0:21:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,女婿大人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:21:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道他一定會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.78,0:22:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是不應該勉強回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野先生  吃早飯吧
