Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊  那傢伙為什麼還在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來
